label: dog
caption: A playful white terrier emerges from a bright blue inflatable tunnel, its ears flapping wildly as it shakes off the excitement of navigating through the winding tube. The tunnel, placed in a backyard play area, is surrounded by lush green grass and a few colorful toys scattered about, adding to the joyful atmosphere. With a wagging tail and a happy bark, the dog prances around the tunnel, eager to continue its fun-filled adventure.
